title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync.
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported JAR file in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time.
EB: The out of sync message should not be displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file in the mentioned scenario.
SR:
1. Navigate to the directory of a project.
2. Export the directory as a JAR file.
3. Place the exported JAR file in the same directory.
4. Attempt to overwrite the exported JAR file a second time.
5. Observe if an out of sync message is displayed.
